<td align="left" width="100%"><font face="verdana,trebuchet,sans-serif" color="black" style="font-size: 11px">RedBrick has posted their first Earthdawn Publications Roster onto their web site for download (see the Publications link to the right). Comments and feedback welcome (see the Contact Us page for details).</font></td>
